description.narrative: The Project Development Objective (PDO) of the PRODEM is to strengthen Government’s capacity to address Niger’s demographic challenge through: (a) enabling the Ministry of Population and Social Reform (MWRS) to design and implement a nationwide multi-sector population program; and (b) increasing general awareness on population and reproductive health issues.
